---
title: Garlic Pork Mince Noodles with bell pepper and pak choi
description: Juicy garlicky pork meatballs and thick saucy udon noodles are the standout components of this dish, but the sticky and sweet sauce comprised of sweet chilli sauce, ketchup manis and soy sauce for a hint of umami is also well worth a shout out!
